subject: Dog Sledding
Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race (Alaska)
lead_paragraph: The four-time champion Jeff King took a narrow lead in the Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race, trading places with his closest rival, Aliy Zirkle.
